  "futureFeaturesDescription": "This is not a closed wishlist. Lustra is infrastructure owned by citizens, so we all have an impact on its development. Join the Civic Evolution community on Reddit, submit ideas, and vote on upcoming features. Let's write the next chapter of democracy together!",
